def acquire_infrastructure():

        "Acquired serverless infrastructure": ["Cloudflare Workers", "AWS Lambda"],

    }
    return infrastructure

infrastructure = acquire_infrastructure()
for category, items in infrastructure.items():
    print(category + ":")
    if isinstance(items, dict):
        for provider, servers in items.items():
            print(provider)
            for server in servers:
                print("-", server)
    else:
        for item in items:
            print("-", item)
